wissens immer größer als der des Wissens. Den Blick auf die dunkle Seite des Nichtwissens zu wagen, ist eine der zentralen Aufgaben, der sich die Geisteswissenschaften heute zu stellen haben.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Nov 2021) 0aIgnorance. 0aMemory in literature. 0aMiscommunication. 4aAllgemeine Literaturwissenschaft. 4aCultural Studies. 4aGlobalisierung. 4aKultur. 4aKulturtheorie. 4aKulturwissenschaft. 4aNichtwissen. 4aWissenskompetenz. 4aWissenssoziologie. 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Popular Culture.2bisacsh  aCultural Studies.  aCultural Theory.  aCulture.  aGeneral Literature Studies.  aSociology of Knowledge.1 aDaiber, Jürgen, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aDotzler, Bernhard J., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aEmig, Rainer, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aGeisenhanslüke, Achim, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aGeisenhanslüke, Achim, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aHammerl, Marianne, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHammwöhner, Rainer, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aMecke, Jochen, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aRott, Hans, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aRott, Hans, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aSauerland, Martin, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aWolff, Christian, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe Gruyterttranscript Highlight Collection Complete Package 2000-2009z9783110463415oZDB-23-TSO08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe Gruyterttranscri